 * Using Rails-like standard naming convention for endpoints.
 * GET     /api/permits              ->  index
 * POST    /api/permits              ->  create
 * GET     /api/permits/:id          ->  show
 * PUT     /api/permits/:id          ->  update
 * DELETE  /api/permits/:id          ->  destroy
